item.title: CVE-2023-26107|2023-03-06T05:00:04.316Z -- n%2Fa -- sketchsvg
item.description: All versions of the package sketchsvg are vulnerable to Arbitrary Code Injection when invoking shell.exec without sanitization nor parametrization while concatenating the current directory as part of the command string.
